To cite teili in publications, please use:

 M. Milde, A. Renner, R. Krause, A. M. Whatley, S. Solinas, D. Zendrikov, N. Risi, M. Rasetto, K. Burelo, V. Leite. teili: A toolbox for building and testing neural algorithms and computational primitives using spiking neurons. Unreleased software, Institute of Neuroinformatics, University of Zurich and ETH Zurich, 2018.

A BibTeX entry for LaTeX users is

@misc{teili,
author		= {Moritz Milde and Alpha Renner and Renate Krause and Adrian M. Whatley and Sergio Solinas and Dmitrii Zendrikov and Nicoletta Risi and Marco Rasetto and Karla Burelo and Vanessa Leite},
title		= {teili: A toolbox for building and testing neural algorithms and computational primitives using spiking neurons},
year		= {2018},
note		= {Unreleased software, Institute of Neuroinformatics, University of Zurich and ETH Zurich}
}

